{"id":459,"parent_id":454,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":459,"title":"Job 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"Job","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","Eliphaz counsels Job: Man is born unto trouble, seek unto God, and happy is the man whom God corrects."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.1","order":"02.19.005.33169"},["b","1"],"Call now, if there be any that will answer thee; and to which of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"saints"],"wilt thou turn?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.2","order":"02.19.005.33170"},["b","2"],"For wrath killeth the foolish man, and envy slayeth the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"silly"],"one."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.3","order":"02.19.005.33171"},["b","3"],"I have seen the foolish taking root: but suddenly I cursed his habitation."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.4","order":"02.19.005.33172"},["b","4"],"His children are far from safety, and they are crushed in the gate, neither",["i","is there"],"any to deliver",["i","them."]],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.5","order":"02.19.005.33173"},["b","5"],"Whose harvest the hungry eateth up, and taketh it even out of the thorns, and the robber swalloweth up their substance."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.6","order":"02.19.005.33174"},["b","6"],"Although affliction cometh not forth of the dust, neither doth trouble spring out of the ground;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.7","order":"02.19.005.33175"},["b","7"],"Yet man is born unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"trouble"],", as the sparks fly upward."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.8","order":"02.19.005.33176"},["b","8"],"I would seek unto God, and unto God would I commit my cause:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.9","order":"02.19.005.33177"},["b","9"],"Which doeth great things and unsearchable; marvellous things without number:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.10","order":"02.19.005.33178"},["b","10"],"Who giveth rain upon the earth, and sendeth waters upon the fields:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.11","order":"02.19.005.33179"},["b","11"],"To set up on high those that be low; that those which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"mourn"],"may be exalted to safety."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.12","order":"02.19.005.33180"},["b","12"],"He disappointeth the devices of the crafty, so that their hands cannot perform",["i","their"],"enterprise."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.13","order":"02.19.005.33181"},["b","13"],"He taketh the wise in their own craftiness: and the counsel of the froward is carried headlong."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.14","order":"02.19.005.33182"},["b","14"],"They meet with darkness in the daytime, and grope in the noonday as in the night."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.15","order":"02.19.005.33183"},["b","15"],"But he saveth the poor from the sword, from their mouth, and from the hand of the mighty."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.16","order":"02.19.005.33184"},["b","16"],"So the poor hath hope, and iniquity stoppeth her mouth."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.17","order":"02.19.005.33185"},["b","17"],"Behold,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"happy"],["i","is"],"the man whom God correcteth: therefore despise not thou the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"chastening"],"of the Almighty:"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.18","order":"02.19.005.33186"},["b","18"],"For he maketh sore, and bindeth up: he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"woundeth"],", and his hands make whole."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.19","order":"02.19.005.33187"},["b","19"],"He shall deliver thee in six troubles: yea, in seven there shall no evil touch thee."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.20","order":"02.19.005.33188"},["b","20"],"In famine he shall redeem thee from death: and in war from the power of the sword."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.21","order":"02.19.005.33189"},["b","21"],"Thou shalt be hid from the scourge of the tongue: neither shalt thou be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"afraid"],"of destruction when it cometh."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.22","order":"02.19.005.33190"},["b","22"],"At destruction and famine thou shalt laugh: neither shalt thou be afraid of the beasts of the earth."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.23","order":"02.19.005.33191"},["b","23"],"For thou shalt be in league with the stones of the field: and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"beasts"],"of the field shall be at peace with thee."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.24","order":"02.19.005.33192"},["b","24"],"And thou shalt know that thy tabernacle",["i","shall be"],"in peace; and thou shalt visit thy habitation, and shalt not sin."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.25","order":"02.19.005.33193"},["b","25"],"Thou shalt know also that thy seed",["i","shall be"],"great, and thine offspring as the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"grass"],"of the earth."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.26","order":"02.19.005.33194"},["b","26"],"Thou shalt come to",["i","thy"],"grave in a full age, like as a shock of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"corn"],"cometh in in his season."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.27","order":"02.19.005.33195"},["b","27"],"Lo this, we have searched it, so it",["i","is;"],"hear it, and know thou",["i","it"],"for thy good."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.1a","order":"02.19.005.33196"},["b","1a"],["span.small","HEB"],"holy ones."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.2a","order":"02.19.005.33198"},["b","2a"],["span.small","OR"],"naive."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.7a","order":"02.19.005.33200"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adversity"},"TG Adversity"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.11a","order":"02.19.005.33202"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mourning"},"TG Mourning"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.17a","order":"02.19.005.33204"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/happiness"},"TG Happiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.17b","order":"02.19.005.33206"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/chastening"},"TG Chastening"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.18a","order":"02.19.005.33208"},["b","18a"],["span.small","HEB"],"smites, bruises."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.21a","order":"02.19.005.33210"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.30"},"D&C 38:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.23a","order":"02.19.005.33212"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.18"},"Hosea 2:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.25a","order":"02.19.005.33214"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/72.16"},"Ps. 72:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.26a","order":"02.19.005.33216"},["b","26a"],["span.small","OR"],"grain."]]}
